         <div type="comments">
            <p>
               <note type="remarks">Subgenre uncertain.</note>
               <note type="remarks">According to <bibl><title corresp="ref:broomhead1962"/><citedRange>273</citedRange></bibl> "[f]our lines written in large ductus, and very clearly preserved".</note>
